if you never go once, who cares is my attitude.  and if there is one time where there isn't a single TF person, that's fine too.  I just wanted to lay one small time when (if the mood saw fit) ppl could all get together, late night style, and get down and dirty with people from many time zones.  I know I got some feedback from torture regarding the topic of time zones, and believe me, i feel their pain. <br>
